//
//  WHAT'S FIXED IN v5.0:
//  ✅ Removed duplicate function definitions (v3+v4 merge conflict)
//  ✅ Category filter now maps short IDs → full names (ac→Air Conditioners etc.)
//  ✅ Sheet schema is ONE source of truth — Image_URL, Simplified_Name always created
//  ✅ fixAllImageUrls / fixAllSimplifiedNames auto-add missing columns before running
//  ✅ enrichAllProducts uses batch write (no per-row sleep, no timeout)
